<p>So far, I&#8217;ve used Bitcoins on more than one occasion as well have some people I personally know. The vetting process between vendors and consumers is reliable but, like I said, you have to be smart with it just like you would with any online transaction. I&#8217;ve yet to end up just being out-and-out thieved via Bitcoin purchases.</p>
